{"tid":1611662,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"屌你正間1點民間記者會冇人講？","createTime":"2019-10-02T04:22:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T04:30:31.000Z","uid":64159,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"00d655ceac3e1cc3514b1c6dd99f0cba869b04be","tid":1611662,"uid":64159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:22:10.000Z","msg":"聯合記者招待會<br />\n.<br />\n民間記者會<br />\n荃灣公立何傳耀紀念中學反修例關注組<br />\n中學生反修例關注組<br />\n九校聯罷<br />\n跨界別抗爭籌備組<br />\n香港大專學界國際事務代表團<br />\n.<br />\n主題：自由之心不死 奈何以槍斃之<br />\n日期：2019年10月2日（星期三）<br />\n時間：下午1:00<br />\n.<br />\n十月一日國殤，魔警血洗全香港，甚至非法在油麻地、荃灣和黃大仙發射六槍實彈，更在荃灣擊中一名中五學生胸口，亦有傳媒拍到有魔警在舉實彈槍時臉露笑容。殺人政權、魔警漸入瘋狂，香港人，是可忍，孰不可忍。<br />\n請於各大網上平台觀看直播。<br />\n.<br />\nJoint Press Conference <br />\n.<br />\nDue to the highly sensitive nature of the matter at hand, this press conference will be held in conjuncture with the Tsuen Wan Public Ho Chuen Yiu Memorial Colledge Anti-ELAB Association, the Hong Kong ANTI-FOO Student Alliance, the Solidary Alliance, the Cross-sector Resistance, and the Hong Kong Higher Institutions International Affairs Delegation. Some co-hosting organisations will also send representatives to speak up during the joint press conference.<br />\n.<br />\nTopic: You Can&rsquo;t Kill Us All<br />\nDate:  2nd October 2019 <br />\nTime:  13:00 <br />\n.<br />\nStay tuned on different live stream on social media platforms.<br />\n<br />\n仆你個街同我推撚上熱門啦！！！"},{"pid":"8e942d004b6f728ec059c48fc7cb499c043c955a","tid":1611662,"uid":20463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:22:50.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"56d08757573c5bc56975cf63474fe31c62a3515e","tid":1611662,"uid":274732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:22:53.000Z","msg":"P牌都要推爆佢！！！！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wh